{"tid":546821,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Amd&Intel  最新資訊","createTime":"2018-02-01T00:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T03:42:49.000Z","uid":58882,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f65afa0f4f3f1f75cafffecc85223adfd7d3c7ff","tid":546821,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:49:46.000Z","msg":"Amd:<br />\n１．AMD宣布在2018年，與主要的雲端伺服商和OEM進一步合作，增加第一代EPYC的應用，並完成第二代Zen 2架構EPYC的設計。<br />\n<br />\n２．7nm Vega也會在今年出現，給深度學習用的。<br />\n<br />\n３．Zen 2架構設計已經完成。在今年會出樣採用7nm製程、基於Zen 2架構的EPYC處理器。（Zen 2會先在伺服器）<br />\n<br />\n據傳：Zen 2將有64核心/128執行緒，L3 256MB，八通道DDR4 3200，PCIe 4.0 128條。<br />\n<br />\n４．預計2018年會發布60+個Ryzen OEM。<br />\n<br />\n５．漏洞Meltdown和Spectre variant 1並不會影響AMD（天生免疫），另外Spectre variant 2對AMD影響也很小。之後出的CPU核心也做了更改，從Zen 2開始，後面的架構將修復Spectre漏洞<br />\n<br />\n６．獨顯的Vega筆電，將進入高階筆電市場。<br />\n<br />\n７．蘇媽稱，顯卡短缺不是因為缺GPU，而是因為顯存的短缺，包括GDDR5和HBM2。目前正在提升產量<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\nAMD 2017財報<br />\n<br />\nQ4收入同比增長了34％，達到14.8億美元，毛利率也保持上季度達成的35％，正好維持盈利。<br />\n<br />\nQ4營收為8200萬美元，高於去年同期的營虧300萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n淨收入為6,100萬美元，也比一年前淨虧損5,100萬美元要好。每股收益在0.06美元。<br />\n<br />\n2017全年收入為55.3億美元，比2016年增長25％，總體毛利率為34％。營收2.04億美元，2016年是虧損3.72億美元。淨收入為4300萬美元，相比之下2016年全年虧損為4.97億美元。<br />\n<br />\n計算與圖形部門，Q4營收為9.58億美元，比去年同期增長了60％。營業收入為8500萬美元，好於一年前2100萬美元的虧損。<br />\n<br />\n企業，嵌入式和半定制部門，本季度收入5.22億美元，比去年同期增長3％，AMD稱這是伺服器貢獻的。營業收入為1900萬美元，低於一年前的4700萬美元。<br />\n<br />\nIntel:<br />\n1. Ice Lake 處理器將於 2019 年出現<br />\n2. Ice Lake 處理器將用 10nm+ 技術製程生產<br />\n3. 新一代 i9 維持18核(14++}<br />\n4. Coffee Lake H  維持4核  意味著notebook不會上6核"},{"pid":"413a581c541f3af996fb84809c863e9e5d9d511d","tid":546821,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:56:50.000Z","msg":"更新amd多一項資訊<br />\n7nm Vega會用台積電<br />\nZen 2會用 GF <br />\nGF 7nm出既時間會比台積電快"},{"pid":"213850ff494ad4ab9a24e95ebd7072b9611e0a7a","tid":546821,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T02:10:52.000Z","msg":"Cannon Lake&nbsp;呢"},{"pid":"c83b6399b9b0c3aecc92da2b03b4818d46d86242","tid":546821,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"213850ff494ad4ab9a24e95ebd7072b9611e0a7a","tid":546821,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T02:10:52.000Z","msg":"Cannon Lake&nbsp;呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T02:13:13.000Z","msg":"只上 notebook  <br />\n維持2核<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eba6332ccca2e049376a18b628b3cd11dc1d79d","tid":546821,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c83b6399b9b0c3aecc92da2b03b4818d46d86242","tid":546821,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"213850ff494ad4ab9a24e95ebd7072b9611e0a7a","tid":546821,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T02:10:52.000Z","msg":"Cannon Lake&nbsp;呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T02:13:13.000Z","msg":"只上 notebook  <br />\n維持2核<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T02:14:56.000Z","msg":"Whiskey Lake會取代 Kaby Lake Refresh 處理器 <br />\n維持4核"},{"pid":"1f0ed28a97b01167cdc9ed3ca3f13e9c4fc974b9","tid":546821,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T02:23:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Cannon Lake&amp;nbsp;呢</blockquote>只上 notebook  <br />\n維持2核<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>Whiskey Lake會取代 Kaby Lake Refresh 處理器 <br />\n維持4核</blockquote><br />\ncore 9th 會係ice lake?"},{"pid":"e8210f50cd758d75c27439d88396851dddb5bb36","tid":546821,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f0ed28a97b01167cdc9ed3ca3f13e9c4fc974b9","tid":546821,